Reynold Xin: CrowdDB: answering queries with crowdsourcing. 61-72.
[6] Richard Hull, Jianwen Su, and Roman Vaculin. 2013. Data management 
perspectives on business process management: tutorial overview. SIGMOD, 
2013.
[7] Serge Abiteboul, Pierre Bourhis, Alban Galland, Bogdan Marinoiu: The 
AXML Artifact Model. TIME 2009: 11-17

